<table border="0" cellpadding="2" cellspacing="0" width="100%">
  <tr>
    <td valign="top" align="left">
    <font face="verdana" size="5">
    Bind Affinity</font>&nbsp;<a href = "../Subscribe.asp?DID=374" ><font face="Verdana" size="2">[Subscribe to this document]</font></a></td>
    <td valign="top" align="left"><img src="http://www.everlore.com/gimages/magic.gif" width="216" height="30" align="right">
    </td>
  </tr>
  <tr>
    <td colspan="2">
    <!--<a href="magic.asp?mode=updateform&amp;ID=374">-->
    <a href="../UserUpdate.asp?ID=374">
    <small><font face="Verdana"><strong>Add New Info Here</strong></font></small>
    </a>
    </td>
  </tr>
  <tr>
    <td valign="top" align="left">
		<font face="verdana" size="2">
		<b>Description:</b> <br>
		This is a VERY useful spell that will change a character's starting point to a new location. As a result, if that person travels a great distance to a different city (i.e., Freeport to Qeynos), and then is bound to that location, and subsequently dies, they will start in the newly bound area. This spell will prevent a lot of aggravation and will make any character that needs it your new best friend!<BR>
<BR>
<B>Location:</B><BR>Magician
		</font>
	 </td>
	 <td rowspan="4" valign="top" align="right">
    
		<table border="1" cellpadding="2" cellspacing="0" width="100%">
			<tr>
				<td valign="top" align="left">
				<font face="verdana" size="2"><b>Spell Stats:</b><hr size="1">
					<table border="0" cellpadding="2" cellspacing="0" width="100%">
						<tr>
							<td width="50%">
							<font face="verdana" size="2">
							Level:<br>
							Rank:<br>
							Target Type:<br>
							Skill:<br>
							Mana:<br>
							Casting Time:<br>



							</font>
							</td>
							<td width="50%">
							<font face="verdana" size="2">
							12<br>
							4<br>
							Target<br>
							Alteration<br>
							100<br>
							6<br>
							</font>
							</td>
						</tr>
					</table>
				</td>
