		</table>

    </td>
  </tr>
  <tr>
    <td valign="top" align="left">
		<font face="verdana" size="2">
		<b>Effects:</b><br>
		Self: Set Home point
Must be grouped to bind another
		</font>
	 </td>
	</tr>
